'''热带风暴阿琳'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Arlene}}）是[[1959年大西洋飓风季|1959年大西洋飓风季]]正式开始前不久形成的一个热带气旋，风暴持续时间很短，于这年5月30日从[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]中部海岸[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，造成一人丧生，另有轻度破坏。天气系统源自5月23日[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]附近的[[东风波|东风波]]，发展速度缓慢，直到5月28日才拥有足够[[对流|对流]]，成为热带风暴阿琳。气旋缓慢增强，于5月30日达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时95公里的最高强度，接下来就因靠近陆地而快速减弱，于当晚以风力时速75公里强度登陆。次日清晨，阿琳的强度已降至现代热带气旋等级中的热带低气压标准。5月31日下午，气旋退化成残留低气压区，最终于6月2日在[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]上空完全消散。

阿琳进入[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]上空后降下暴雨，局部降雨总量超过300毫米。[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]的梅里尔前后三天共测得344毫米雨量，是风暴产生降水最多的所在。暴雨在路易斯安那州引发轻度洪灾，造成的财物损失总额约为50万美元（1959年美元）。气旋还间接导致[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]近海一名男子因遭遇大浪丧生。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Arlene 1959 track.png}}
热带风暴阿琳源于5月23日位于[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]附近的[[东风波|东风波]]，在朝西面经过[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的同时缓慢发展，于5月25日成为[[低气压|低气压区]]。截至5月27日，低气压区已进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]，次日有船只遭遇降雨，还在低气压区内部发现闭合下层环流。<ref name="MWR">{{cite journal | author = Gordon E. Dunn and Staff | title = Monthly Weather Review for 1959 | year = 1959 | publisher = Weather Bureau Office | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200709/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1959.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1959.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>据气象机构估算，次日早上低气压区已在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]东南偏南方向约480公里海域增强成热带风暴阿琳，估计风速已达到每小时65公里，此时1959年大西洋飓风季尚未正式开始。气旋获命名前是以每小时16到24公里的速度朝西北方向移动。风暴朝向在27日当天继续保持，前进速度还提高到每小时19至24公里。<ref name="ADVSPG1">{{cite report | author = New Orleans Weather Bureau | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Advisories, Page One | year = 1959 | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224243/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim3.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim3.gif | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>5月29日，阿琳转向西进，移动速度逐渐放缓，并在当天夜间基本停止前进<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="ADVSPG3">{{cite report | author = New Orleans Weather Bureau | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Advisories, Page Three | year = 1959 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215748/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim5.gif | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim5.gif | format = GIF | date =  }}</ref>。

风暴向北飘移，估计在抵达路易斯安那州[[拉法叶_(路易斯安那州)|拉法叶]]以南约240公里洋面时达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度<ref name="ADVSPG4">{{cite report | author = New Orleans Weather Bureau | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191225/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim6.gif | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Advisories, Page Four | year = 1959 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim6.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | date =  }}</ref>。但经过飓风季后的重新分析，气象部门认定阿琳是在登陆前不久达到持续风速每小时95公里的最高强度<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160810161332/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | date = 2016-07-06 | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | archivedate = 2016-08-10 }}</ref>。气旋逼近海岸，然后开始因陆地的影响而减弱。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]21点，风暴从拉法叶东南方向约65公里处登陆，登陆时的风速在气象机构当时的记载中为每小时85公里，但经季后重新分析调整为每小时75公里<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="ADVSPG5">{{cite report | author = New Orleans Weather Bureau | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Advisories, Page Five | year = 1959 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303173342/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim7.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim7.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | date =  }}</ref>。阿琳至此成为路易斯安那历史上登陆日期最早的热带气旋<ref name="MWR" />。进入陆地上空后，风暴迅速减弱成热带低气压，再于5月31日下午进一步消退成残留低气压区<ref name="ADVSPG6">{{cite report | author = New Orleans Weather Bureau | title = Tropical Storm Arlene Advisories, Page Six | year = 1959 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183904/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim8.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1959/arlene/prenhc/prelim8.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF | date =  }}</ref>。气旋残留继续在[[美国南部|美国南部]]徘徊，直至6月2日在[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]上空完全消散<ref name="HURDAT" />。虽然原本的低气压天气系统已经消亡，但更北面的[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]上空又形成新的[[温带气旋|气旋中心]]，新系统快速朝东北方向移动，其中不具备热带天气系统特征，掠过[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]南部海岸后又进入[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]上空，最终于6月3日失去踪影<ref name="HPC">{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | title = Tropical Storm Arlene 1959 Rainfall Map | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/arlene1959filledrainblk.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064618/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/arlene1959filledrainblk.gif | date =  }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Arlene_1959_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
热带气旋形成前，[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]南部的东西两侧沿海地区就因低气压区形成而收到大风警告和[[小型船只公告|小型船只公告]]<ref name="MWR" />。低气压区于次日升级成热带风暴阿琳，小型船只公告的生效范围大幅扩张，从德克萨斯州[[阿瑟港_(德克萨斯州)|阿瑟港]]的[[萨宾帕斯_(德克萨斯州)|萨宾帕斯]]（{{lang|en|Sabine Pass}}）一直延伸到佛罗里达州[[圣马克_(佛罗里达州)|圣马克]]，同时路易斯安那州的[[摩根城_(路易斯安那州)|摩根城]]到密西西比州[[帕斯卡古拉_(密西西比州)|帕斯卡古拉]]收到烈风警告。烈风警告中估计气旋会产生0.6至1.2米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]。<ref name="ADVSPG1" />截至5月29日，路易斯安那州所有港口的船只都已收到通知，建议不要离港出海。许多居民对两年前的[[飓风奥黛丽|飓风奥黛丽]]记忆犹新，所以在得知阿琳来袭后便从沿海地区撤离。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = The News and Tribune | date = 1959-05-31 | title = Arlene Pushing Into Louisiana}}</ref>该州[[阿桑普申堂区_(路易斯安那州)|阿桑普申堂区]]的[[皮埃尔_(路易斯安那州)|皮埃尔]]（{{lang|en|Pierre}}）有50户家庭疏散到地势更高的地点<ref name="UPI1">{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = Aiken Standard and Review | date = 1959-06-01 | title = Storm Arlene Dumps Heavy Rain on La.}}</ref>，另据政府官员称，[[弗米利恩堂区_(路易斯安那州)|弗米利恩堂区]]也有25户生活在低洼地区的人家撤离<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = ''Anderson Herald'' | date = 1959-05-31 | title = Storm Strikes at Louisiana, Begins Fading}}</ref>。阿琳登陆前不久，佛罗里达州[[彭萨科拉_(佛罗里达州)|彭萨科拉]]以南地区的小型船只公告停止生效，新的预警范围从彭萨科拉延伸到德克萨斯州[[加尔维斯敦_(德克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]。烈风警告生效范围也向西调整，从加尔维斯敦延伸到路易斯安那州的[[格兰德艾尔_(路易斯安那州)|格兰德艾尔]]。<ref name="ADVSPG3"/>

风暴登陆时产生每小时90公里的大风，阵风时速达到120公里。陆地上测得的最低[[气压|气压]]为999.7[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.52[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]，经四舍五入后定为1000毫巴（百帕，29.53英寸汞柱），风暴最低气压数据便由此而来。路易斯安那州的威克斯岛（{{lang|en|Weeks Island}}）和欧费尔角（{{lang|en|Point Au Fer, Louisiana}}）测得0.9米高的风暴潮。<ref name="MWR" />路易斯安那州东南沿海地区普降暴雨，[[新奥尔良路易斯阿姆斯特朗国际机场|莫圣特国际机场]]在24小时里就降下277毫米雨量<ref name="OSB1">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = Ocala Star Banner | date = 1959-06-01 | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | title = Storm Arlene Blowing Itself Out In Center Of Mississippi Today | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=L8swAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5QQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1913,1416601&dq=storm+arlene&hl=en | page = 10 | archive-date = 2020-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020095253/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=L8swAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5QQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1913%2C1416601&dq=storm+arlene&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。机场的控制塔水深约有0.61米，迫使交通管制人员迁到正在建设的新塔<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Sarasota Journal | date = 1959-06-01 | accessdate = 2016-09-09 | title = Spent Arlene Wends Way In Mississippi | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DAMdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7ooEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5767,101150&dq=arlene+mississippi&hl=en | page = 10 | archive-date = 2020-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020095259/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DAMdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7ooEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5767%2C101150&dq=arlene+mississippi&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。全州以[[霍玛_(路易斯安那州)|霍玛]]降水最多，达334毫米<ref name="MWR" />。部分沿海城镇因狂风导致树木倒塌，输电线缆中断，引发局部地区停电<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1959-05-31 | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | title = Storm Arlene, Losing Power, Hits La. Coast | page = 1 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5uYNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8HYDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6796,4892305&dq=storm+arlene&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020095304/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5uYNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8HYDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6796%2C4892305&dq=storm+arlene&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

风暴期间，新奥尔良的多条主干道因洪灾封闭<ref name="OSB1" />，至少有100户民居被风暴淹没。[[巴吞鲁日_(路易斯安那州)|巴吞鲁日]]有数十人在家园被淹后搭乘救护车和旅行车前往更加安全的地点。<ref name="UPI1" />附近的密西西比州降雨范围基本局限在东南部多个县内，但降雨量依然很高，最高达到344毫米<ref name="HPCGC">{{cite report | author = David M. Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall for the Gulf Coast | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcgulfcoast.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304092617/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcgulfcoast.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。气旋消散后，残留低气压区还在继续产生降水，影响范围延伸到[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]境内，导致部分河流泛滥和农作物受损，但总体破坏程度很轻。整场风暴一共造成价值50万美元（1959年美元）的损失，加尔维斯敦近海有一名男子因遭遇大浪溺毙，属阿琳间接导致的人员丧生事故。<ref name="MWR" />低气压区在美国东南部上空消散后，阿琳的温带残留还在[[中大西洋地区|中大西洋地区]]和[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]产生中等程度降水<ref name="HPC" />。

